{"tid":2276664,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：政棍／神棍總能用虛假的議題，製造假希望，香港被送去攬炒。即使世道不古，我們自有自己的天下。","createTime":"2020-11-08T03:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T04:54:11.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"108dad5cf83b7be65bec184bb34811ecd9c2a73f","tid":2276664,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QoAyeVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQoAyeVQ.jpg&h=479a0221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰：<br />\n這幾年的跌宕，圍繞的主題只有一個：「愛惜熱狗」。<br />\n在亂世之下，虛偽的言辭太多，亦是救世政棍／神棍的天堂。<br />\n無他，是因他們總能夠利用虛假的議題，製造假希望，叫人沉醉在「矯情造作」之中，違反常情，虛渡光陰。香港就這樣斷葬。<br />\n香港被送去攬炒，但我們不是。未來我們更要珍惜同道中人,，即使世道不古，我們自有自己的天下。<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想。"},{"pid":"4b450914cf8731868ada59ab8f6f651ea7bc1221","tid":2276664,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"鑬鈔鈀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fa8170c28ff53119726ac59a3c4e51476e6718","tid":2276664,"uid":42283,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"熱狗乜黨仲有任務比你呀"},{"pid":"aabfae5ee27a704de727b459f5b5456c9524ccda","tid":2276664,"uid":150912,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"d0fa8170c28ff53119726ac59a3c4e51476e6718","tid":2276664,"uid":42283,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"熱狗乜黨仲有任務比你呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦<br />\n美國民主黨仲有乜撚野任務俾你班泛民"},{"pid":"59b716594d2c1a45e2b1e6d772c65130cce8f88b","tid":2276664,"uid":42283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aabfae5ee27a704de727b459f5b5456c9524ccda","tid":2276664,"uid":150912,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"d0fa8170c28ff53119726ac59a3c4e51476e6718","tid